                                 devFront



Settings
========

Settings page is only available from the address 127.0.0.1

Projects:
- Name: project name to display
- URL: project url (eg. http://localhost/foo , /foo/ , http://example.com)
- Image: Project image filename 
    must be found in project_images folder

Folders:
- Name
- Path: folder path
    preferably absolute path
- Pattern: Pattern to create link from folder name
    Using sprintf the script substitues %s with the foldername in the pattern.
    
    eg. #1
    path = /var/www/foo/bar
    pattern = /foo/bar/%s/

    eg. #2
    doxygen-generated documentations are in /var/www/doc/
    path = /var/www/doc/
    pattern = /doc/%s/html/